{"tid":1609613,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［爆料］蘋果記者講述今日北角炮台山情況","createTime":"2019-10-01T15:01:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T17:48:36.000Z","uid":204398,"like":83,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"5d21a0f819cbc69c56e7a0458cb042c65d560964","tid":1609613,"uid":204398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:01:28.000Z","msg":"啱啱直播講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日本身有班人就喺SOGO對出<br />\n班人都係冇咩gear<br />\n記者有問佢哋打住做咩<br />\n佢哋回應話打算留多留就走<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係突然之間有人提出北角有白衣人</span></span></strong><br />\n但係個邊冇哨兵同埋冇人影到有手足俾人打<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">姐係完全冇任何根據</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n個一陣記者都覺得唔應該去<br />\n但係根據記者專業操守，佢哋係唔應該阻止手足所做嘅決定<br />\n就同一班守護孩子既人跟左去<br />\n<br />\n去到之後<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">突然之間前面有人跑過嚟同佢哋講有狗車</span></span></strong><br />\n由於個班係冇咩gear既人，所以佢哋都開始退後<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">但係好戲劇性地</span></span></strong><br />\n後面突然之間有十幾架狗車響晒燈同安<br />\n就大量防暴衝落車就捉咗10幾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">但係重點由頭到尾都完全唔見有白衫人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家出去個陣要有啲理性思考<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果冇任何證據證明某地方出事</span></span></strong><br />\n請大家慎重考慮信息真確性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51eeeb42ac6fba416623f4dc7cf3797be4047caa","tid":1609613,"uid":204398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:02:18.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"7b89775f0fa8aa276e23cc9be668a3db56e2112b","tid":1609613,"uid":204398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":